Title

The Kelowna Courier

Dates

1904-1949

Place of Publication

Kelowna (B.C.)

Publisher

Kelowna Courier

Frequency

Biweekly

Description

Contains past publications of the Kelowna Daily Courier from its founding in 1904 to 1949. This newspaper was issued first weekly, and then bi-weekly, serving Kelowna, the Okanagan Centre, and Peachland. The newspaper went through multiple name changes, including 'Kelowna Clarion and Okanagan Advocate' and the 'Kelowna Courier and Okanagan Orchardist.' Missing Issues: Volume 1 Issue 10, Volume 2 Issues 17-21 and 23, Volume 5 Issues 19 and 23, and Volume 14 Issue 13.
